query: SELECT v.id, v.title, v.fileId, f.filename, f.mimeType, f.url FROM videos v JOIN files f ON v.fileId = f.id WHERE f.filename LIKE '%PXL_20260122%' ORDER BY v.id DESC LIMIT 5;
